sentence: Brad Shoup of Stereogum surmised that, thanks to the Ramones ' praise for the group, many punk, pop punk, or punk-adjacent artists showed influence from the Beach Boys, noting cover versions of the band's songs recorded by Slickee Boys, Agent Orange, Bad Religion, Shonen Knife, the Queers, Hi-Standard, the Descendents, the Donnas, M.O.D., and the Vandals.
